Ikinagagalak kitang makilala.

50:43.375 --> 50:44.666
Magical.

50:54.041 --> 50:55.333
At ngayon

50:55.416 --> 50:57.333
dumating ang mahirap na bahagi.

50:58.125 --> 51:01.666
